00:06:00.027 --> 00:06:02.863 align:start position:30% line:-1
別の宇宙も見せられます

00:06:02.963 --> 00:06:05.632 align:start position:27% line:-1
実際の被写体と違う世界です

00:06:06.366 --> 00:06:07.968 align:start position:39% line:-1
